        "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
        "body": "At one point cudf (possibly before libcudf!) used a stream pool for gather operations. Each gather is independent, so we can launch all the kernels on separate streams and synchronize them with an event on the input stream. I would love to reimplement this approach and see if it can improve the performance. See also #12086.",
